  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个医疗数据流的架构图，展示从患者记录到HIPAA合规存储的完整流程。整体分为三个主要阶段：扫描层、解析层和合成层。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SCANNER",
        "PARSER",
        "COMPOSER"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，三个主模块。我先确认一下命名——扫描层用HealthTech_LabAnalyzer，解析层是HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault，合成层叫HealthTech_EMR_Sync，这样符合你们的命名规范吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SCANNER",
        "PARSER",
        "COMPOSER"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，这三个子系统名称准确。先从扫描层开始：里面需要三个节点，S1和S3都是HealthTech_PatientRecords，S2是HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S1",
        "S2",
        "S3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，扫描层三个节点已放置。S1和S3都是患者记录，S2是诊断引擎。接下来画连接关系？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S1",
        "S2",
        "S3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "S1和S2都要汇聚到S3，形成数据汇总。然后S3要输出到解析层的P1。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S1",
        "S2",
        "S3",
        "P1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "扫描层内部连接完成，S3也连到P1了。现在构建解析层PARSER，四个节点对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P1",
        "P2",
        "P3",
        "P4"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "解析层四个节点：P1和P2都是HealthTech_EMR_Sync，P3是HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault，P4是HealthTech_LabAnalyzer。P1接收来自S3的数据，然后流向P2。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P1",
        "P2",
        "P3",
        "P4"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "P1到P2的连接已添加。P2需要分叉到P3和P4吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P2",
        "P3",
        "P4"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，P2要同时输出到P3和P4。P3走合规存储路线，P4返回实验室分析做闭环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P2",
        "P3",
        "P4"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "P2的分叉连接完成。现在处理合成层COMPOSER？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "COMPOSER",
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "C3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "合成层三个节点：C1是HealthTech_PatientRecords，C2和C3都是HealthTech_EMR_Sync。C1和C2都要汇聚到C3。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "C3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下：C1和C2都是输入端，C3是最终汇聚点？那C1和C2的数据来源分别是？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C1",
