      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "好的。另外我发现P4的标签是HealthTech_LabAnalyzer，这和SCANNER的子图名称重复了，这是有意为之吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
